{"lemma":"قَصُّ","slug":"قَصُّ","root":"ق.ص.ص","root_slug":"ق-ص-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-ص-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"قَصُّ","root":"قصص","pos":"V","occurrence_count":20},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":12},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n35697","n35698"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%82%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to cut (“to remove and place in memory in order to paste at a later time”)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to clip off, to shear, to cut off"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be near death, to impend"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bring near to death"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to narrate, to relate, recount, to tell, to impart, to communicate (news, a story, etc.)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make a speech, to lecture, to recite"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to follow one's tracks"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of قَصَّ (qaṣṣa, “to clip, narrate, etc.”) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"clipping, shearing, cutting off"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"top or middle of the chest"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gypsum"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew קָצַץ (katsáts), from the root ק־צ־ץ."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n35697","headword_ar":"قَصٌّ","root":"qS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaSN","text_ar":"قَصَصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What is cut,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clipped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shorn, of the wool"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a sheep. (M, K, TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"quSaASapN","text_ar":"قُصَاصَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  Also, both words, (S, M, A, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSoqaSN","text_ar":"قَصْقَصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, A, K) of anything: (M:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) called in Persian"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sr synh","text_ar":"سر سينه"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sarosiynaho","text_ar":"سَرْسِينَهْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", applied to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pit at the head of the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and such is the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaS","text_ar":"قَصَص"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the sheep or goat, &c.: (S:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"middle thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bone thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) of a man or other animal; (TA;) [i. e. the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sternum;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft bone into which are set the cartilaginous ends of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seven upper pairs of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ribs, in the middle of the breast:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiSaASN","text_ar":"قِصَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[a reg. pl. of the first]. (K.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^alozamu laka","text_ar":"هُوَ اَلْزَمُ لَكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino $uEayoraAti qaS~ika","text_ar":"مِنْ شُعَيْرَاتِ قَصِّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa A^alozamu bika mino $aEaraAti","text_ar":"هُوَ اَلْزَمُ بِكَ مِنْ شَعَرَاتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~ika","text_ar":"قَصِّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSaSika","text_ar":"قَصَصِكَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is more closely adherent to thee than the little hairs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hairs, of thy breast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.:] because as often as they are cut they grow [afresh]: (As, TA:) meaning, he will not separate himself from thee, nor canst thou cast him from thee: applied to him who denies his relation: and also to him who denies a due that is incumbent on him. (Sgh, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, the same three words, (the first and ↓ second accord. to the TA, and the ↓ third accord. to the K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaSiySN","text_ar":"قَصِيصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of growth of the hair of the breast."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~N","text_ar":"قَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK, and so in one place in a copy of the M, and in the TA,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiS~N","text_ar":"قِصٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in one place in a copy of the M) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~apN","text_ar":"قَصَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiS~apN","text_ar":"قِصَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaS~N","text_ar":"جَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (JK,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiS~N","text_ar":"جِصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Gypsum;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~apN","text_ar":"قَصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jS~","text_ar":"جصّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb) in the dial. of El-Hijáz: (S:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~apN","text_ar":"قَصَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiS~apN","text_ar":"قِصَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) the latter on the authority of IDrd, (TA,) and said by Aboo-Bekr to be with kesr, but by others said to be with fet-h, (Seer, TA,) are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaS~apN","text_ar":"جَصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiS~apN","text_ar":"جِصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", ns. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaS~N","text_ar":"جَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiS~N","text_ar":"جِصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) or signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stones of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jS~","text_ar":"جصّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gypsum"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiSaASN","text_ar":"قِصَاصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[reg. as pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~apN","text_ar":"قَصَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~aASN","text_ar":"قَصَّاصٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. form of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~N","text_ar":"قَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaS~N","text_ar":"جَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiS~N","text_ar":"جِصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"], a subst., like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jay~aArN","text_ar":"جَيَّارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which is nearly, if not exactly, syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiyrN","text_ar":"جِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jiaS~N","text_ar":"جَِصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M, L.) In a trad. of Zeyneb, occurs this expression:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY maloHuwdapK","text_ar":"عَلَى مَلْحُودَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaAqaS~apF","text_ar":"يَاقَصَّةً","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O gypsum upon buried corpses!"},{"kind":"text","text":"] by which she likens the bodies of the persons addressed to tombs made of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jS~","text_ar":"جصّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and their souls to the corpses contained in the tombs. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","TA","S","A","Lth","As","JK","Msb","Seer"]},{"entry_id":"n35698","headword_ar":"قِصٌّ","root":"qS","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaS~N","text_ar":"قَصٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last signification; the latter in three places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}